        "Id": "de458e08-4eb7-44c7-b72f-24f7986c4f46",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The bastard child",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ANCESTRAL_BULLDOG",
        "PublicId": "128699858839",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5403294c-5390-46ba-a246-4bb6108253c0).Image",
        "Description": "Rosie Jones is in trouble, Patrick Carlisle slept with her and got her pregnant. His mother Emma was informed by Alice Rogers to whom Rosie confied. Emma Carlisle hired a private investigator to find proof that Emma manage to beguiled Patrick into having sex to get a child who could be in the line of succession. 47, This young girl just want out. You need to eliminated everyone who know of the secret and make it look like an accident.",
        "GameVersion": "8.1.0.0",
